OL,6,FA scaled-back day and night parade is
OL,7,Fexpected to take place with smaller
OL,8,Ffloats through town on the usual
OL,9,FBattle days - Friday 8 and Saturday 9
OL,10,FAugust.
OL,12,FOrganisers plan to make it a free
OL,13,Fcommunity event with exhibitors given
OL,14,Fsmall grants from the government's
OL,15,Ffunding to cover their costs.
